      "title": "My latest cartoon for New Scientist",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/e8608a5c93d34f66d3a856c6d68522f9/447feddbadf92a81-b5/s640x960/5b0acb6b85f2e7d855b48b85b90b63b3bd70f7ee.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"961\" data-orig-width=\"1446\" alt=\"Title: Artemis 2&#10;&#10;Panel 1: &#10;Moon &quot;Hi guys!&quot;&#10;Artemis 2&quot;Hello Moon!&quot;&#10;&#10;Panel 2:&#10;Moon &quot;You're not landing&quot;&#10;&#10;Panel 3:&#10;Artemis 2 &quot;Just orbiting this time.&quot;&#10;Moon &quot;Oh.&quot;&#10;&#10;Panel 4:&#10;Artemis 2, leaving &quot;But we'll be back soon.&quot;&#10;&#10;Panel 5:&#10;Moon thinking...&#10;&#10;Panel 6:&#10;Moon, sadly &quot;That's what they said in 1972.&quot;\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/e8608a5c93d34f66d3a856c6d68522f9/447feddbadf92a81-b5/s75x75_c1/aee586a2e5306dbe00ad68fa6ce2c98a5fff0ccc.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/e8608a5c93d34f66d3a856c6d68522f9/447feddbadf92a81-b5/s100x200/441f163cb7990439e68b2546303091b6d360a40a.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/e8608a5c93d34f66d3a856c6d68522f9/447feddbadf92a81-b5/s250x400/99ca79c50245b8d198bc8ee853860f1c5b245df2.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/e8608a5c93d34f66d3a856c6d68522f9/447feddbadf92a81-b5/s400x600/906cd555a12c84f697320db8b94c411bbab685d0.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/e8608a5c93d34f66d3a856c6d68522f9/447feddbadf92a81-b5/s500x750/e37a8adf09416694d806d9154d0273989a5bf86a.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/e8608a5c93d34f66d3a856c6d68522f9/447feddbadf92a81-b5/s540x810/8f5f6c1bdc2b0238939cee569505ac987b01faf2.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/e8608a5c93d34f66d3a856c6d68522f9/447feddbadf92a81-b5/s640x960/5b0acb6b85f2e7d855b48b85b90b63b3bd70f7ee.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/e8608a5c93d34f66d3a856c6d68522f9/447feddbadf92a81-b5/s1280x1920/6ef994db37adb99af4b1b3a6c63a34a952ebaa48.jpg 1280w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/e8608a5c93d34f66d3a856c6d68522f9/447feddbadf92a81-b5/s2048x3072/6f149ec5dd037297558411ee7d1bdf5150fb0673.jpg 1446w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"/>"
