      "title": "A cartoon for #IndieBookstoreDay, which is tomorrow!\nGet out to your local bookstore! ",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/10ea43f57f576725addf3316eacae5b3/7493f0f7f196b949-5c/s640x960/c1a4b7bebc96ae18282ca9b13a16e64b7a709e8b.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"587\" data-orig-width=\"1200\" alt=\"&#10;Title: Specialist delivery services available from local bookshops &#10;&#10;A chart showing the services folowing this structure:  &#10;G. Genre &#10;H. How To order &#10;M. Method of Delivery&#10;&#10;G. Romance &#10;H. A trusted servant dispatched with a secret letter &#10;M. A brooding Aristocrat on a Black horse&#10;&#10;G.  Murder-mystery &#10;H.  A telephone call from within a locked room&#10;M.  A bookseller/ gentleman detective &#10;&#10;&#10;G. Science fiction&#10;H. A robot bearing a holographic Message&#10;M. Teleported from an orbital data platform &#10;&#10;G. Horror &#10;H. Screams. Awful, bloodcurdling screams.&#10;M. An evil thing. Horrible beyond Comprehension &#10;&#10;G; Fantasy&#10;H. Runes engraved on an enchanted Elven sword &#10;M. A postal goblin riding on a talking raven&#10;\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/10ea43f57f576725addf3316eacae5b3/7493f0f7f196b949-5c/s75x75_c1/d92c4e99853206cbb1a6fb67667ad11c670986f9.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/10ea43f57f576725addf3316eacae5b3/7493f0f7f196b949-5c/s100x200/8b78226f9660565e7b9a8309e5e2f055df09ee9e.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/10ea43f57f576725addf3316eacae5b3/7493f0f7f196b949-5c/s250x400/bd73fd0ae33d7054fb2368f6cfdb29018a7300ea.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/10ea43f57f576725addf3316eacae5b3/7493f0f7f196b949-5c/s400x600/f25b1ec5084a9244d4bc7f9880765c089d91d975.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/10ea43f57f576725addf3316eacae5b3/7493f0f7f196b949-5c/s500x750/c716b16ae80914bae785651706cf86d9101c47dd.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/10ea43f57f576725addf3316eacae5b3/7493f0f7f196b949-5c/s540x810/66da598e6b0d91926a70527b58a27cebcba46ceb.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/10ea43f57f576725addf3316eacae5b3/7493f0f7f196b949-5c/s640x960/c1a4b7be