      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/9d0d02e43037f0509de4cb79f5dbf47c/19d2b3c1581a08f8-64/s640x960/f7e7595bee2028d9fbad2bdbf117fa311d361119.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"961\" data-orig-width=\"1000\" alt=\"A panel from the cartoon quoted below\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/9d0d02e43037f0509de4cb79f5dbf47c/19d2b3c1581a08f8-64/s75x75_c1/c04b523b0fc0f037650c84a118f8db9b505222fd.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9d0d02e43037f0509de4cb79f5dbf47c/19d2b3c1581a08f8-64/s100x200/094d4d7a4b8d0be300baf38e29a4f174130626fa.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9d0d02e43037f0509de4cb79f5dbf47c/19d2b3c1581a08f8-64/s250x400/31140fb64fac169feaca036c206ced20e2eff742.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9d0d02e43037f0509de4cb79f5dbf47c/19d2b3c1581a08f8-64/s400x600/96b8dba3fc4cfed0e3af3aa5ef1b272d31eb9af3.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9d0d02e43037f0509de4cb79f5dbf47c/19d2b3c1581a08f8-64/s500x750/7221790e366d6b3760acd226064e8897ea43a1e3.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9d0d02e43037f0509de4cb79f5dbf47c/19d2b3c1581a08f8-64/s540x810/4b9c7d548d4cef375dcc98664b9cf14fe6cd4651.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9d0d02e43037f0509de4cb79f5dbf47c/19d2b3c1581a08f8-64/s640x960/f7e7595bee2028d9fbad2bdbf117fa311d361119.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9d0d02e43037f0509de4cb79f5dbf47c/19d2b3c1581a08f8-64/s1280x1920/3abd6646554a7c6d72843cdedb4760ea56b70fc8.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"/>\n<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/1a9b654c1b29e3e8970e80c8aab51f94/19d2b3c1581a08f8-b3/s640x960/e94445668bef5ac6e57551493ad48946ee8baa77.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"961\" data-orig-width=\"1000\" alt=\"Small sketchbook doodles in black ink showing a small child, cloaked figures, an isolated house and a forest.\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/1a9b654c1b29e3e8970e80c8aab51f94/19d2b3c1581a08f8-b3/s75x75_c1/9b32a59914fe6a4c3ae29bd43897585dee41e0ef.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/1a9b654c1b29e3e8970e80c8aab51f94/19d2b3c1581a08f8-b3/s100x200/e246179497d667e1ecaf240c1ed8332eb1df2fc9.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/1a9b654c1b29e3e8970e80c8aab51f94/19d2b3c1581a08f8-b3/s250x400/96e178b79acfa66127e7ae594127f7434f468a4b.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/1a9b654c1b29e3e8970e80c8aab51f94/19d2b3c1581a08f8-b3/s400x600/31d0cf767c1ed0bf7c0afa539e7f44011814798f.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/1a9b654c1b29e3e8970e80c8aab51f94/19d2b3c1581a08f8-b3/s500x750/76d18337996c544785558cc61b315e17704b6b2d.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/1a9b654c1b29e3e8970e80c8aab51f94/19d2b3c1581a08f8-b3/s540x810/8fd35d5e709f571dbf35c92c29444d6bc0caf8d5.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/1a9b654c1b29e3e8970e80c8aab51f94/19d2b3c1581a08f8-b3/s640x960/e94445668bef5ac6e57551493ad48946ee8baa77.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/1a9b654c1b29e3e8970e80c8aab51f94/19d2b3c1581a08f8-b3/s1280x1920/7b07b7949253abd8bc5db4801eb5a55943fd8e63.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"/>\n<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/3dd921e6fbe170480640ee9c6be059bd/19d2b3c1581a08f8-7f/s640x960/7ff7188cfa412b30ac06eb68b30f29457f056053.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"961\" data-orig-width=\"1000\" alt=\"A strip cartoon drawn in black ink.&#10;&#10;Two hooded figures with lamps approach a moonlit, isolated cottage.&#10;A woman answers the door.&#10;We have come for the child, says the hooded figure&#10;So soon? she asks&#10;It is time, says the hooded figure.&#10;The woman is distraught. We should never have got him a library card!&#10;What is done cannot be undone, says the hooded figure&#10;We couldn&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;t see the harm! We just wanted him to enjoy reading! &#10;For most, it ends there, says the hooded figure, turning away and walking into the wilderness&#10;Oh lord, What have I done! says the woman,&#10;the child walks past her and out into the darkness with them.&#10;Do not cry mother. &#10;I am a writer now.\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/3dd921e6fbe170480640ee9c6be059bd/19d2b3c1581a08f8-7f/s75x75_c1/a01dbcf67e097dfba2361d62184a845ef0c72084.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/3dd921e6fbe170480640ee9c6be059bd/19d2b3c1581a08f8-7f/s100x200/b94de6a4c911889431ca640dfc5ff1ffdb86061a.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/3dd921e6fbe170480640ee9c6be059bd/19d2b3c1581a08f8-7f/s250x400/1c6f9d4d2a0dd865f22261a956b445326ada33f5.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/3dd921e6fbe170480640ee9c6be059bd/19d2b3c1581a08f8-7f/s400x600/a759d7d998a0fc8a9bab805c86a0a0b5f4bff249.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/3dd921e6fbe170480640ee9c6be059bd/19d2b3c1581a08f8-7f/s500x750/e92de82855cf752a3b732afc63983054c8b37d46.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/3dd921e6fbe170480640ee9c6be059bd/19d2b3c1581a08f8-7f/s540x810/e92506d9e718ec3df9cce62568b5ca08e1dc228e.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/3dd921e6fbe170480640ee9c6be059bd/19d2b3c1581a08f8-7f/s640x960/7ff7188cfa412b30ac06eb68b30f29457f056053.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/3dd921e6fbe170480640ee9c6be059bd/19d2b3c1581a08f8-7f/s1280x1920/3bde8046d4526203b06172e10622a5573ea94171.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"/>"
